p.seg:
When they came to Jesus, they saw the man  
					    who had been possessed by the legion of demons, sitting there, dressed  and in his right mind;
					    and they were afraid.

Then the chief priests, the teachers of the law and the elders looked 
					     for a way to arrest him because they knew he had spoken the parable against them. But they were afraid of the crowd;
					     so they left him and went away.
